<div class="container r-bars">
    <div class="col-md-12 top-grid">
        <h4>Why you should chose our store...</h4>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 t1">
        <h5><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-bitcoin"></span>We use Bitcoin</h5>
        <p>We process payments using Bitcoin. This makes our store pretty unique comparing to other businesses in this category. Bitcoin is fast, safe and easy! If you need help to process a payment using Bitcoin, don't hesitate to contact us!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 t2">
        <h5> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-certificate"></span> Cerfified products</h5>
        <p>When you buy our products you are always issued a certificate to prove your good is the real deal. If you have any damages on your product please bring your product together with the certificate for free and fast assistance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 t3">
        <h5><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-comment"></span>Feedback</h5>
        <p>Are you afraid how the product will look like in real life? Do you wanna know what other people think about a specific product? Our store provides the ability to comment on a specific product. Use it as guidence when deciding what to buy!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 t4">
        <h5><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok-sign"></span>Payments</h5>
        <p>We want you to feel safe when using our store. We intentionally made payments using several different methods possible. Paypal, Mastercard, Bitcoin... you name it!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 t5">
        <h5><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-hourglass"></span>Delivery time</h5>
        <p>Thanks to our close cooperation with UPS are products are delivered with speed! Products are always processed for shipping the next day! All to insure a fast delivery.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 t6">
        <h5><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-plus"></span>And more...</h5>
        <p>This store was recently opened which means are feautures are not in use right now. More feautures are planned to be released soon. Please hold on!</p>
    </div>
</div>

